{
  "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "给你一座迷宫，从入口走到出口，你会怎么找路？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.22,
      "size": 35568,
      "text": "一种办法是四面八方同时铺开，像水波一样层层漫过去。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "另一种是认准一个方向一直走，走不通再退回来换条路。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "这两种策略就是广度优先搜索和深度优先搜索。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "bfs",
      "line_id": "bfs-1",
      "filename": "bfs-bfs-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/bfs-bfs-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "广度优先用一个队列，先进先出，从起点开始。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "bfs",
      "line_id": "bfs-2",
      "filename": "bfs-bfs-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/bfs-bfs-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "每次取出一个格子，把它没走过的邻居都排到队尾。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "bfs",
      "line_id": "bfs-3",
      "filename": "bfs-bfs-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/bfs-bfs-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32400,
      "text": "于是访问顺序像同心圆，一圈一圈地向外扩散。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "dfs",
      "line_id": "dfs-1",
      "filename": "dfs-dfs-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/dfs-dfs-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.19,
      "size": 34992,
      "text": "深度优先改用栈，后进先出，总是先探最新发现的格子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "dfs",
      "line_id": "dfs-2",
      "filename": "dfs-dfs-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/dfs-dfs-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "它沿着一条路蜿蜒深入，直到撞墙或走进死胡同。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "dfs",
      "line_id": "dfs-3",
      "filename": "dfs-dfs-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/dfs-dfs-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "这时就回溯到上一个岔口，换一个方向继续往下钻。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "shortest",
      "line_id": "short-1",
      "filename": "shortest-short-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/shortest-short-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.04,
      "size": 32688,
      "text": "因为 BFS 是一层层推进的，先到达的一定步数更少。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "shortest",
      "line_id": "short-2",
      "filename": "shortest-short-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/shortest-short-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "所以它第一次碰到出口时，走的正是最短的那条路。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "shortest",
      "line_id": "short-3",
      "filename": "shortest-short-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/shortest-short-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "深度优先可不保证，它找到的路往往绕了远。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "切换到 BFS，看颜色如何从起点同心扩散开来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "再切到 DFS，看它怎样一头扎进去、碰壁又折返。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "BFS 用队列层层扩散，DFS 用栈一路到底。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "前者在无权图上给出最短路，后者胜在实现简洁省空间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "bfs-dfs",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/bfs-dfs/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.79,
      "size": 28656,
      "text": "同一座迷宫，两种走法各有妙用，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
  "total_duration": 35.16,
  "total_size": 562608
}